00077 void test()
00078 {
00079     if (os_) *os_ << setprecision(14);
00080 
00081     // initialize frequency data
00082 
00083     FrequencyData fd;
00084     for (const Datum* p=data_; p!=data_+dataSize_; ++p)
00085         fd.data().push_back(FrequencyDatum(p->frequency, p->intensity));
00086     fd.observationDuration(.768);
00087     fd.analyze();
00088     
00089     // "peak detection"
00090 
00091     Peak detected;
00092     detected.frequency = fd.max()->x;
00093     if (os_) *os_ << "detected: " << detected << endl;
00094 
00095     // create estimator
00096     
00097     FrequencyEstimatorPhysicalModel::Config config;
00098     auto_ptr<FrequencyEstimatorPhysicalModel> fe(FrequencyEstimatorPhysicalModel::create(config));
00099 
00100     // get estimate and check answer
00101 
00102     Peak estimate = fe->estimate(fd, detected);
00103     if (os_) *os_ << "estimate: " << estimate << endl;
00104 
00105     unit_assert_equal(estimate.frequency, 159454.98465, 1e-4);
00106 }
